<section id="Exporting_a_Widget" remap="TID_41926">
	<title>Exporting a Widget</title>
	<para>
		You can share widgets between appliances using the export and import features.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Export a Widget</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Cloud Intelligence</guimenu><guisubmenu>Reports</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In the <guimenu>Import/Export</guimenu> accordion, click <guilabel>Widgets</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In the <guilabel>Export</guilabel> area, select the widgets that you want to export.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>Export</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>